Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:25.04,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fscx50\fscy50\bord2\an8\fnArial Black\c&H565350&\3c&HEEEEEC&\pos(321.5,95.5)}{Welcome!  Members of Kessoku Band\N}{\fs15}{We Hope Your Time Here Heals You in Both Mind and Body}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.41,0:02:11.71,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{This... is it, isn't it?}Là... đây nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:15.05,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{It... does say "Kessoku Band," right?}Nó ghi ban nhạc Kessoku kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:18.08,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Did she mention her house was a ryokan?}Nhà cậu ấy... là nhà trọ hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:22.33,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I'm not sure. It just looks like \Na normal house to me.}Không biết nhưng bề ngoài là nhà bình thường mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.88,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:25.04,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,Thôi thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:29.20,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{We're here, Bocchi-chan!}Bọn chị đến nè Bocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:30.53,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Hello!}Xin chào!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.53,0:02:33.15,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{C-Coming!}D-Đến ngay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:36.42,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord2\fs14\fnTimes New Roman\c&H454133&\3c&HABA19D&\pos(317,213.5)}{Sergeant For a Day}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:40.99,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Y-Yaaaay!}Yê!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:44.14,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,W-W-Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:01.46,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I liked dark, cramped spaces,}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:03.83,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{so I'd bury my face deep in my hood}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:06.21,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{My eyes resented the heartless world,}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:09.96,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{but yearned for love}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:16.60,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I liked being soaked by the rain,}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.60,0:03:18.97,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{because my face looked better clouded over}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:21.61,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I pretended to be afraid of the storm}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:24.44,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{while waiting for the sky to burst}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:31.40,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{Strum through the light's distortion}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:35.82,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I want to make thunder roar}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:41.62,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{Drum beyond the pain}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:45.75,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{What can I do? This fierce \Npounding is out of control}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:51.81,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{Strum in a harmonizing quartet}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:55.80,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I want to cause a revolution}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:04:01.81,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{Drum in a lamenting forte}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:06.56,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{What can I do? My savage \Nnature is beyond wild}
