Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:30.21,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Are you having fun, Bocchi-chan?}Bocchi, em có vẻ vui nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:31.34,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Y-Yeah...}V-Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:33.25,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I b-b-bombed...}T-Thất bại rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:35.05,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Isn't that nice?}Cơ mà vui ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:38.03,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Gotoh-san's made it clear how much \Nshe's been looking forward to this too!}Chứng tỏ Gotoh rất mong chờ ngày hôm nay đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:41.39,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Kita-san knows the kindest words \Nto soothe my bombed soul.}Kita luôn nói những lời tử tế để xoa dịu mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:43.22,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{C-Come in.}M-Mời vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.42,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Okay!}Ừm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:47.85,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fscx50\fscy50\bord2\an8\fnArial Black\c&H565350&\3c&HEEEEEC&\pos(321.5,95.5)}{Welcome!  Members of Kessoku Band\N}{\fs15}{We Hope Your Time Here Heals You in Both Mind and Body}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:45.96,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Coming in!}Xin phép!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:50.10,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Gotoh-san, these are for you.}Gotoh nè, quà chào hỏi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:51.87,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Please enjoy them with your family.}Hãy ăn cùng gia đình nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:53.20,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Wh-What?}H-Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:55.36,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,C-Cảm ơn cậu...{Th-Thank you...}
