Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:15.62,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Besides...}Với cả...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.59,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{There's nothing tying you guys together.}Chẳng có cảm giác gì là Kessoku cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:19.46,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,Chị ấy nhất định sẽ nói thế!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:22.74,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{You get it? We're not here to play around!}Hiểu chứ? Hôm nay đến đây không phải chơi đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:22.13,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Th-This way...}L-Lối này...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:31.22,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnTimes New Roman\bord2\c&H000000&\3c&H4A4A4A&}{Welcome to Chez Gotoh}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:36.16,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I-I'm sorry. I'll put it all away.}E-Em sẽ dọn dẹp ạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:39.89,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{W-Well, we could play around a }{\i1}{little}{\i0}{!}À thì... chơi chút cũng được...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:41.27,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Yes, I'd love that!}Ừm, vậy đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:44.35,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{W-Well then, I'll fetch the drinks.}V-Vậy em đi lấy nước.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:46.47,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Please make yourselves at home.}Hai người cứ tự nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:47.86,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Thanks!}Cảm ơn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:53.66,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{But wow, she really went \Nall-out with the decorations!}Cơ mà... em ấy trang trí dữ thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:57.22,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{There's nothing here besides the guitar \Nand effects unit, though.}Cơ mà chỉ có mỗi cây ghita với mấy đồ này thôi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:58.29,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Yeah...}Ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:02.17,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I just assumed her room would have \Na bit more of a rock feel to—}Em cứ nghĩ phải có cảm giác rock--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:10.05,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(402,1)\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\c&H010301&\3c&H595959&\pos(322.5,304)\fay-0.18}{Sealed}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:07.67,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Is this... rock?}Đó là... rock ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:10.05,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Yeah, it's pretty rock!}Ừm, rock đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:13.11,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I w-wonder if there's \Nanything else rock about i—}C-Còn cái gì mang cảm giác rock không nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:14.10,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Ow!}Đau...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:18.94,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Huh? Why does she have so \Nmany copies of our ProPho?}Ủa? Sao nhiều ảnh nhóm vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:21.69,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\fs18\c&H010301&\3c&H595959&\frz350\pos(318.5,23.5)}{Sealed }{\3c&H1E534F&\frz10}{Sealed }{\3c&H595959&\frz335}{Sealed}
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.94,0:06:21.69,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\fs18\c&H010301&\3c&H423132&\frz10\pos(322,19.5)}{Sealed }{\3c&H423132&\frz330}{Sealed }{\3c&H1E534F&\frz310}{Sealed}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:28.06,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I don't know what's going on, \Nbut it seems pretty darn rock!}Chị không hiểu lắm nhưng rock thật đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:30.45,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{She's got blown-up ones too!}Có cả loại lớn nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:37.54,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,342)\an8\fnTimes New Roman\bord2\c&H000000&\3c&H4A4A4A&}{Welcome to Chez Gotoh}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:34.50,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{She had this picture stuck up \Nall over her room.}Chị ấy dán đầy phòng luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:37.30,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{She said she really liked it!}Chị ấy thích bức này lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:42.20,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{But Mom told her to take them down\Nbecause they were hurting her eyes.}Nhưng mẹ không cho dán khắp nhà tại đau mắt lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:47.42,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{And we put those seals up \Nwhen Sis was possessed before!}Và nhà em đã phong ấn thứ đó trước khi chị bị chiếm hữu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:49.84,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{That should just about cover it!}Giải thích kết thúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:53.80,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Wait, are you Gotoh-san's sister?}Em là em gái Gotoh hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.48,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{Yes! A pleasure to meet you.}Vâng! Rất vui được gặp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:57.30,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{I'm Futari Gotoh.}Em là Gotoh Futari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:58.73,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{The dog's Jimihen.}Chó là Jimihen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.46,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I hope barley tea's okay.}Trà lúa mạch ổn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:08.12,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Or would they prefer a trendier drink?}Hay là loại xịn hơn?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:10.57,Default,Nijika/Kita,0,0,0,,{So cute!}Dễ thương ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.54,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Sorry to keep you guys wa—}Xin lỗi vì đã...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:15.95,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{Hey, will you play the \NMunions song on guitar?}Nè, chị chơi Munions bằng ghita đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:18.80,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I'll practice so I can do it \Nthe next time I come by.}Vậy lần tới chị sẽ luyện tập và chơi cho em.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:21.00,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{You gotta! When's the next time you come by?}Hứa nhé. Lần tới chị sẽ đến hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:23.29,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I-Is this...}Đ-Đây là...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.46,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Jimihen's a friendly little guy!}Jimihen thân thiện ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:31.42,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Th-They're getting along so well, \Nthere's no room left for me...}H-Họ đang rất thân thiết khi không có mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:33.78,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Huh? Bocchi-chan?}Bocchi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:34.80,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Gotoh-san?}Gotoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:37.28,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{A five-year-old and a dog \Nhave better social skills than me.}Một đứa nhóc 5 tuổi và con chó\N còn có kĩ năng giao tiếp hơn mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:39.49,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{Sis is frozen up again.}Chị lại đứng im rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:42.00,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{F-Futari. Wh-What are you doing here?}F-Futari, sao em ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.25,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Wh-Where are Mom and Dad?}Ba mẹ đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:44.45,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{Shopping.}Đi mua đồ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:48.71,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I-I-I've got grown-up things to talk about, \Nso please go play with Jimihen.}Giờ chị đang bận nên em ra chơi với Jimihen đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:51.04,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{Aw, no fun!}Không, chán lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:53.56,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I don't mind having Futari-chan here.}Tớ không thấy phiền đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:54.61,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Yeah, same!}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:56.20,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Y-Y-Y-You can't!}K-K-Không được!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:59.40,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I c-c-can't whoop it up if my sister's here!}E-Em ấy còn nhỏ nên không hiểu đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:02.00,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Bocchi-chan, you've been \Nwhooping it up with us all this time?}Bocchi-chan, em lúc nào cũng thế còn gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:03.28,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I beg of you!}Làm ơn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:05.33,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,Hãy ra chơi với Jimihen đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:09.14,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{You can have an ice pop from the freezer.}Chị sẽ cho em kem trong tủ lạnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:13.92,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{Well, it is what it is!}Thiệt tình à.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.90,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{You've got such a sisterly bond!}Chị em thân thiết ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:20.52,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{How did you get that\Nfrom what just happened?}Vừa rồi là thân thiết hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:24.67,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Now, let's design those T-shirts!}Giờ thì quyết định mẫu thiết kế nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:26.48,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(417,1)\shad2\bord4\fnComic Sans MS\fs28\c&H0B36B5&\3c&HEFF3F5&\4c&H863D5B&\pos(.108,81)\frz19.18}{L}{\c&HC85918&}{e}{\c&H9784F6&}{t}{\c&H4FA91A&}{'}{\c&H6785E8&}{s }{\c&H1C42BA&}{D}{\c&HC85918&}{r}{\c&H9784F6&}{a}{\c&H4FA91A&}{w}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:26.48,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Feel free to use these!}Dùng sổ tay này vẽ thoải mái nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:27.85,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Okay!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:28.46,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Okay...}Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:30.56,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{We could just slap\Nour logo on there,}Chúng ta có thể đính logo lên,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:33.57,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{but I'd love to sell the shirts as merch, too!}nhưng chị cũng muốn bán áo để kiếm tiền.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:36.12,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{N-Nijika-chan is so hungry for merch!}C-Chị nhắm đến nó từ đầu sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:39.54,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{So if you have any other great ideas, \NI might use those as well!}Nên mấy em có ý tưởng gì thì hãy nói ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:42.01,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Okay! Let's do our best, Gotoh-san!}Rồi! Cố gắng nào Gotoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:43.25,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{R-Right!}V-Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:45.89,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I have to impress the others for once!}Mình phải thể hiện điểm mạnh mới được!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:49.42,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{C'mon, take that stuff off \Nbefore you try to look serious!}Em đừng nghiêm túc với bộ dạng đó được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:52.16,Default,Naoki,0,0,0,,{What? They really came?}Hả? Đến thật á?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:53.47,Default,Michiyo,0,0,0,,{Really? For real?}Thật luôn?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:54.74,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{Yeah!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:56.83,Default,Michiyo,0,0,0,,{These friends aren't just the imaginary kind?}Không phải bạn tưởng tượng hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:08:58.64,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{Yeah, yeah!}Vâng vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:05.02,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fs20\an8\fnTimes New Roman\bord2\c&H6C7270&\3c&HE7E9F2&}{Welcome to Chez Gotoh}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:03.52,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{All done!}Xong rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:05.02,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Let me see!}Để chị em.
