Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:54.68,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{Hey, hey, Kita-chan!}Nè nè Kita-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:55.72,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{What's this?}Gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:59.00,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{That's my favorite heartwarming movie!}Là một bộ phim ấm áp mà chị thích đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:02.11,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I've always wanted to watch that one!}Chị cũng muốn xem nó lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:03.62,Default,Michiyo,0,0,0,,{Wanna watch it all together?}Vậy thì cùng nhau xem đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:05.25,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{Yes, please!}Tán thành!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:07.93,Default,Naoki,0,0,0,,{Great idea! What fun!}Tuyệt đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:14.54,DefaultTop,Naoki/Futari,0,0,0,,{Yeah! So fun! So fun! Yeah!}Vui ghê! Vui ghê!
