Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.91,0:14:38.02,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{And yet...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:42.04,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{That's right! We still need to design \Nour T-shirts for the concert.}Phải nhỉ! Chúng ta vẫn chưa nghĩ ra mẫu áo nhóm.
