Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:43.25,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Kita-chan, don't actually respond!}Kita, em không cần trả lời đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:44.93,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{E-Excuse me...}X-Xin lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:47.71,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Hey, Bocchi-chan's back?}Em quay lại rồi hả?
